Santosh Bank â€“ Customer Churn Dashboard
Objective: Analyze churn behavior and business insights using Power BI.

Tools Used: Excel&Power BI (visualization, DAX, data modeling)

Key Insights:
Churn rate is highest among customers with 1 product and tenure < 3 years.

Male customers show higher churn rate compared to female.

Germany has the highest churn among the three countries.

Features Built:
KPI cards (Total Customers, Total Churned, Churn Rate %)

Interactive filters: Age Group, Gender, Geography

Visualizations:

Churn by Gender (bar)

Churn by Geography (donut)

Churn trend by Age (line)

Churn by Tenure Category

Average Balance by Age Group (bar)
